    <item>
      <title>Tinder揭露了嬉戏的AI聊天机器人，以提高参与度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/tinder-unveils-playful-ai-chatbots-in-bid-to-boost-engagement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Match Group Inc.的Tinder推出了一款应用程序内游戏，邀请用户与人工智能的聊天机器人调情，这是通过促进用户参与度恢复约会应用程序增长的更大努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/tinder-unveils-playful-ai-chatbots-in-bid-to-boost-engagement</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软银为美国的AI增长寻求创纪录的165亿美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/softbank-seeks-record-16-5-billion-loan-for-ai-projects-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，软银集团公司正在寻求高达165亿美元的贷款，以帮助在美国的人工智能投资资金，这将是技术投资者的有史以来最大的有史以来以美元计价的最大的设施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/softbank-seeks-record-16-5-billion-loan-for-ai-projects-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 03:38:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当Lutnick推动更大的投资时，美国筹码处于困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-chip-grants-in-limbo-as-lutnick-pushes-for-bigger-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[商务部长霍华德·卢特尼克（Howard Lutnick）表示，他可以扣留筹码的筹款活动，因为他推动公司以联邦半导体补贴为基础扩大其美国项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-chip-grants-in-limbo-as-lutnick-pushes-for-bigger-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 02:38:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Openai最终筹集了400亿美元的资金，价值3000亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/openai-finalizes-40-billion-funding-at-300-billion-valuation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Chatgpt背后的人工智能公司Openai表示，它已完成了一轮融资，该融资将从Softbank Group Corp.和其他投资者带来3000亿美元的估值，包括筹集的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/openai-finalizes-40-billion-funding-at-300-billion-valuation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:39:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>GlobalFoundries探索与台湾UMC的合并</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/globalfoundries-is-said-to-explore-merger-with-taiwan-s-umc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士说，GlobalFoundries Inc.正在探索与台湾芯片制造商联合微型电子公司的潜在合并，这是一项长期交易的一部分，旨在创建一个更具弹性的老年人半导体制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/globalfoundries-is-said-to-explore-merger-with-taiwan-s-umc</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 18:01:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SpaceX推出了由加密投资者资助的Polar SpaceFlight</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/spacex-set-to-launch-polar-spaceflight-funded-by-crypto-investor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的SpaceX发起了第一个人类太空飞行任务，飞越地球的极地地区，由加密货币投资者Chun Wang资助和指挥。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/spacex-set-to-launch-polar-spaceflight-funded-by-crypto-investor</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 17:09:53 GMT</pubDate>
